                            <h5>Disclosure of your information
                            </h5>
                            <p>We may share your personal information with any member of our group, which means our subsidiaries, our ultimate holding company and its subsidiaries, as defined in section 1159 of the UK Companies Act 2006.
                            </p>
                            <p>We may share your information with selected third parties including:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    Business partners, suppliers and sub-contractors for the performance of any contract we enter into with them or you.

                                </li>
